{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FetchEvent.replacesClientId","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/replacesClientId","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API\">Service Worker API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent\"><code>FetchEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/FetchEvent\"><code>FetchEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/clientId\"><code>clientId</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/isReload\"><code>isReload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/PreloadResponse\"><code>preloadResponse</code></a></li><li><em><code>replacesClientId</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/request\"><code>request</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/resultingClientId\"><code>resultingClientId</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/respondWith\"><code>respondWith()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ExtendableEvent\"><code>ExtendableEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Service Workers API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Cache\"><code>Cache</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CacheStorage\"><code>CacheStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\"><code>Client</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clients\"><code>Clients</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ExtendableEvent\"><code>ExtendableEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InstallEvent\"><code>InstallEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/serviceWorker\"><code>Navigator.serviceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/NotificationEvent\"><code>NotificationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicSyncEvent\"><code>PeriodicSyncEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicSyncManager\"><code>PeriodicSyncManager</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerContainer\"><code>ServiceWorkerContainer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>ServiceWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SyncEvent\"><code>SyncEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SyncManager\"><code>SyncManager</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowClient\"><code>WindowClient</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent\"><code>FetchEvent</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>replacesClientId</code></strong> 読み取り専用プロパティは、ページナビゲーション中に置き換えられる<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\" title=\"クライアント\"><code>クライアント</code></a>の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/id\" title=\"id\"><code>id</code></a> です。</span></p>\n\n<p>例えば、ページ A からページ B に移動する場合、<code>replacesClientId</code> はページ A に関連するクライアントの id です。 <code>about:blank</code> のクライアントは置き換えられるのではなく再利用されるため、<code>about:blank</code> から別のページに移動するときは、空の文字列になることがあります。</p>\n\n<p>さらに、フェッチがナビゲーションでない場合、<code>replacesClientId</code> は空の文字列になります。 これは、ナビゲーションの直前に間もなく置き換えられるクライアントにアクセス/通信するために使用できます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>myReplacedClientId</em> = <em>fetchEvent</em>.replacesClientId;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'fetch'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>replacesClientId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/ServiceWorker/#dom-fetchevent-replacesclientid\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Service Workers<br><small lang=\"ja\">replacesClientId の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.FetchEvent.replacesClientId","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/replacesClientId/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API/Using_Service_Workers\">Service worker の使用</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/sw-test\" rel=\" noopener\">サービスワーカーの基本的なコード例</a>（英語）</li>\n <li><a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://jakearchibald.github.io/isserviceworkerready/\" rel=\" noopener\">ServiceWorker の準備はできていますか？</a>（英語）</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\">Web worker の使用</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"FetchEvent インターフェイスの replacesClientId 読み取り専用プロパティは、ページナビゲーション中に置き換えられるクライアントの id です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FetchEvent.replacesClientId","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/fetchevent/replacesclientid","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/fetchevent/replacesclientid/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent","title":"FetchEvent"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent/replacesClientId","title":"FetchEvent.replacesClientId"}],"pageTitle":"FetchEvent.replacesClientId - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}